CatDescriptText: Cutline of image published in Pittsburgh Courier newspaper, January 9, 1960, pg. 3, reads: "Honored by NAPE - Congressman William S. Moorehead [Moorhead], Democrat, 28th District, received an honorary membership in National Alliance of Postal Employes [Employees] this week. NAPE's vice president James Bradley made the presentation.  The occasion marked the kickoff drive of the NAPE for new members. - Harris Photo."
TitMainTitle: Congressman William S. Moorhead receiving honorary membership in National Alliance of Postal Employees (NAPE) from James Bradley
